-- France, Europe Face Real Terror Threat, Interior Minister Hortefeux Says
-- B y   H e l e n e   F o u q u e t
-- 2010-10-05T13:16:25Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-05/france-europe-face-real-terror-threat-interior-minister-hortefeux-says.html
France and the rest of Europe face a
“real threat” of terror attcks, Interior Minister Brice
Hortefeux said in the country’s parliament today.  Hortefeux also confirmed that French police today arrested
three people “directly implicated” in terrorism.  To contact the reporter on this story:
